{"tid":1994100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果追問陶輝醜聞 李家超速閃：你向警方查詢啦","createTime":"2020-04-29T08:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T08:41:33.000Z","uid":5195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"138b33d2e145211fa3b08ed51e90e234b184571d","tid":1994100,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T08:41:33.000Z","msg":"保安局局長李家超今早現身立法會走廊時，被問到陶輝是否違規住在碧水新村的寮屋或牌照屋，以及為何記者昨日採訪要遭到警員拘捕調查時，李家超全程拒作回應，只說：「我而家去立法會先」。李會後趁三名局長回應傳媒有關檢疫問題的查詢期間，趁機離開會立法會。其間《蘋果》記者上前追問他為何要拘捕兩名《壹週刊》記者時，身為保安局局長的李家超只稱：「你向警方查詢啦」。<br />\n<br />\n全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200429/SY2336Q2UTAVIHWBKKSUM3TA3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200429%2FSY2336Q2UTAVIHWBKKSUM3TA3U%2F&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjwxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=2bdda60f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200429%2FSY2336Q2UTAVIHWBKKSUM3TA3U%2F&h=1d8fd632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200429/SY2336Q2UTAVIHWBKKSUM3TA3U/</a>"}]}